PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 945) establishing a Maximum Residue Limits for Clopyralid (a systemic, post emergent herbicide effective in controlling Canadian thistle and other broadleaf weeds and is registered under the Pest Control Products Act for use in Canada on a wide variety of food and forage crops) in flax to be used in food products.
